# Running Graphs
[TOC]

This library contains classes for launching graphs and executing operations.

The [Getting Started With TensorFlow](../../get_started/get_started.md) guide has
examples of how a graph is launched in a [`tf.Session`](../../api_docs/python/tf/Session.md).
